author: rooneg
msg: On the ra-replay-dev branch: Fix some error messages in the mod_dav_svn
side of the replay code, add authz support, and fix a bug that resulted
in a crash when you tried to replay a change you didn't have the right
to see over ra_dav.
* subversion/mod_dav_svn/replay.c
(dav_svn__replay_report): Set up an authz baton and callback, fix up
some log messages for when we hit errors.
* subversion/libsvn_ra_dav/replay.c
(end_element): Don't destroy the directory pools unless we have some
in the stack, it can be empty in the case where we aren't allowed to
see any of the changes.
